。家庭主申请人可以自愿按网站提示，通过互联网端在线或现场向本市相关公证机构申请办理公证。办理完成公证并已提交公证书的，可在 1-3 个工作日后登录小客车指标网站查看核查结果。 家庭申请人填报的申请信息应当真实、准确，对所填报信息的真实性负责。对于家庭申请人填报错误信息导致的亲属关系或婚姻状况核查不通过等后果，由其自行承担。北京今年首期普通车摇号，超六成指标被「无车家庭」摇中"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-d5952653505b4979a3adf9f843bf3749_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "73 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/539829090"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIg6+G5dDB7YwBEAMaCDgyMjQzNjU0IJaV35UGMAM4ggFAEHIJNTM5ODI5MDkweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1656227275.3290172", "card_id": "Q_275244312", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 2452}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "人类现在有没有可能是宇宙中最高等的文明？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-b1f497108f9e39accf9ef4e467e90ee2_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "73 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/275244312"}}, "attached_info": "ClYIg6+G5dDB7YwBEAMaCDIzNDQxMTA0IJ+hldcFMJ8BOKZ1QBFyCTI3NTI0NDMxMngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA8gETCAESD2RvbWFpbl9vcGVyYXRvcg=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "18_1656227275.3294857", "card_id": "Q_539403470", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 24}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价手游《明日方舟》外服即将增添英语配音及韩语配音？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-cb2c2a2dd9d7a3a7ae157c48c45c735e_b.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "72 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/539403470"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Ig6+G5dDB7YwB